title: Test
summary: This grouped bar chart has 3 categories of Category on the x axis representing 2 groups: Anorexia nervosa, and Bulimia nervosa.
Averaging these 2 groups, the highest category is found for Category Full recovery with a mean value of 45.5.
Followed by Improvement with a mean value of 30.0.
The lowest category is observed at Chronically ill that has a mean value of 21.5
showing a difference of 71.6% with the maximum value.
In case of Full recovery, Anorexia nervosa shows more dominance than any other Category with a value 46.0 and it has the lowest value 20.0 in Chronically ill.
